You can explore your data in a Snowflake warehouse without loading data into CRM Analytics or preparing it in datasets. CRM Analytics Direct Data for Snowflake lets you set up a live connection to the Snowflake schema you want to explore.

When to Use CRM Analytics Direct Data for Snowflake
To run analysis on your Snowflake data, you can use CRM Analytics Direct Data for Snowflake or Snowflake input connectors or a combination of the two.

Create a Live Connection to Snowflake
After you complete setup, CRM Analytics Direct Data for Snowflake lets you run queries on the dataset associated with the connection in real time. You can also build dashboard charts and tables based on the queries you run on Snowflake data.

Explore Data Directly in Snowflake 
It helps to be familiar with these tips and considerations when working with Direct Data for Snowflake.
title: Exploring Data Directly in Snowflake
